Privacy Policy for Prayer Chain
Last Updated: May 24, 2025

This Privacy Policy describes how Prayer Chain ("we," "our," or "us") operates our mobile application, "Prayer Chain" (the "App"), a prayer chain service.

We want to be absolutely clear: Prayer Chain does not collect, store, or process any personal information from its users.

By using the App, you acknowledge and agree to this policy.

1. Information We Do Not Collect
Prayer Chain is designed to function without collecting any personal data or information from you. This includes, but is not limited to:


2. How We Do Not Use Your Information
Since we do not collect any information, we naturally do not use your information for any purpose, including:

Creating or managing accounts

Complying with legal obligations related to user data

3. How We Do Not Share Your Information
As no information is collected by Prayer Chain, no information is shared with other users, service providers, or for any legal or business transfer reasons. Your data remains entirely on your device.

4. Data Security
Given that Prayer Chain does not collect or store any personal information, traditional data security measures for user data are not applicable to our operations. Any information you input remains solely on your device.

5. Data Retention
Since no personal information is collected by Prayer Chain, there is no user data for us to retain.

6. Your Data Protection Rights
As Prayer Chain does not collect or process any of your personal data, the typical data protection rights (such as the right to access, rectification, erasure, etc.) do not apply in relation to our operation of the App. Your control over any data you generate within the App rests entirely on your device.

7. Children's Privacy
Our App does not collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13. Therefore, we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.

9. Contact Us
